Release xde-session-1.9 released 2018-10-06
-------------------------------------------

git tag -n100 -l 1.9

1.9             Pre-Release 1.9

    This is another pre-release of the xde-session package. It includes the
    playing of sound effects when locking and unlocking the screen. Also,
    window manager launch scripts now turn the NumLock key off before
    launching the window manager. (Some window managers defeat some mouse
    actions and key bindings when the NumLock key is on.)

    As usual, included is an autoconf tarball for building the package from
    source. Please report problems to the issues list on github.

git shortlog -e -n -w80,6,8 1.8...1.9

Brian Bidulock <bidulock@openss7.org> (6):
      post release update
      add sound support to lock screen
      don't play sound on initial screen unlock
      turn numlock off when launching window managers
      fix gcc 8.2 warnings of redundant strncpy/strncat
      update release files


